---
title: Southeast Asian Chicken & Honey-Soy Veggies with Jasmine Rice & Japanese Mayo
description: Watch out because our lovely spiced chicken is going to turn some heads tonight! With all the umami, but pan-fried instead of deep-fried, this is a quick and easy dinner that's going to blow your mind.
